ActPublic Service Labour Relations Act
SubjectNational Film Board - Syndicat général du cinéma et de la télévision, Local 4835 (CUPE) ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving that the National Film Board ENTER INTO A COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the Syndicat général du cinéma et de la télévision, Local 4835 (CUPE), in respect of its employees in the Technical category, which agreement is from July 1, 2018 to June 30, 2022.
